* And you must be

33:06.218 --> 33:08.054
* The plug

33:08.087 --> 33:11.057
* Oh, yeah.

33:11.090 --> 33:13.392
(cheering)

33:13.425 --> 33:15.061
COOKIE:
Yes! Okay...

33:15.094 --> 33:16.162
-That was really good.
-Okay.

33:16.195 --> 33:17.963
-I like that.
-All right. All right.

33:17.996 --> 33:21.133
(clears throat)
That was amazing.

33:21.167 --> 33:23.502
It was beautiful, it was real,
it was from the heart.

33:23.535 --> 33:25.237
PORSHA:
We got our Alpha.

33:28.607 --> 33:31.043
WOMAN:
Happy birthday, Bella!

33:31.077 --> 33:33.512
-Hakeem, yeah!
-(applause and cheering)

33:33.545 --> 33:35.013
Make some noise!

33:37.583 --> 33:40.552
-(whooping, whistling,
cheering, applause) -Welcome.

33:40.586 --> 33:43.089
Welcome. Welcome. Welcome.
Listen, I want to thank y'all

33:43.122 --> 33:47.359
for coming out to celebrate my
princess's first birthday party.

33:47.393 --> 33:49.928
Bella Lyon!

33:49.961 --> 33:51.863
(applause and cheering)

33:54.900 --> 33:56.335
This for you, baby.

33:56.368 --> 33:58.537
-Let's hit it.
-Yay.

33:58.570 --> 34:00.906
(synthesizer plays intro
to "Let's Go Crazy")

34:02.974 --> 34:05.711
-HAKEEM: Dearly beloved...
-(applause and cheering)

34:05.744 --> 34:09.248
We're gathered here today to get
through this thing called life.

34:11.083 --> 34:13.219
Electric word, life.

34:13.252 --> 34:14.753
It means forever, and that's

34:14.786 --> 34:17.723
a mighty long time,
but I'm here to tell you

34:17.756 --> 34:20.126
there's something else.

34:20.159 --> 34:22.461
The afterworld.

34:22.494 --> 34:25.531
A world
of never-ending happiness.

34:25.564 --> 34:27.566
You can always see the sun,

34:27.599 --> 34:30.636
day or night.

34:30.669 --> 34:32.704
(applause and cheering)

34:32.738 --> 34:35.040
So when you call up that shrink
in Beverly Hills--

34:35.073 --> 34:37.809
you know the one--
Dr. Everything'll Be All Right--

34:37.843 --> 34:40.146
instead of asking him
how much of your time is left,

34:40.179 --> 34:43.149
ask him how much of your mind,
baby.

34:43.182 --> 34:45.151
'Cause in this life,
things are much harder

34:45.184 --> 34:46.752
than in the afterworld...

34:46.785 --> 34:50.656
Now, y'all know, uh, Prince
don't celebrate no birthdays?

34:50.689 --> 34:53.325
-Ain't that right, Tyka?
-See? That's what I said.

34:53.359 --> 34:56.428
That's exactly what I told him,
but what do I know?

34:56.462 --> 34:58.063
I'm nothing more
than a guest here.

34:58.096 --> 34:59.298
* Go crazy

34:59.331 --> 35:02.100
* Punch a higher floor

35:02.134 --> 35:05.271
(whoops)

