36:13.071 --> 36:14.706
* Oh, no, let's go

36:14.740 --> 36:18.043
* Crazy

36:18.076 --> 36:20.011
-* Say let's go crazy
-* Go crazy

36:20.045 --> 36:22.681
-* Let's go
-* Let's go

36:22.714 --> 36:24.149
-* Let's go, let's go
